" Mimic Emacs Line Editing in Insert Mode Only
inoremap <C-A> <Esc>g^i
inoremap <C-B> <Left>
inoremap <C-E> <Esc>g$a
inoremap <C-F> <Right>
inoremap <C-P> <Up>
inoremap <C-N> <Down>
inoremap <C-d> <Del>
inoremap <C-K> <Esc>lDa
inoremap <C-U> <Esc>d0xi
inoremap <C-Y> <Esc>Pa
" inoremap <C-X><C-S> <Esc>:w<CR>

